    "updated_at": "2016-07-18T16:49:11Z",
    "body": "So, I found the cause of this issue. I was experimenting with improving the perceived performance of the load time by not immediately showing the window. When i removed this code, the resize rules worked. Here is the code...\n\n```\nmainWindow.loadURL('file://' + __dirname + '/static/index.html')\nmainWindow.hide()\n\nsetTimeout(() => {\n  mainWindow.show()\n}, 350)\n```\n"
